def create_matrix(rows, cols, default_value = 0):
    """To ma trn vi rows hng v cols ct"""
    return [[default_value for _ in range(cols)] for _ in range(rows)]


def matrix_multiply(A, B):
    """Nhn ma trn A v B"""

    # Trng hp B l vector
    if not isinstance(B[0], list):
        # Chuyn B thnh ma trn ct
        B = [[b] for b in B]
    
    # Ly kch thc ca ma trn
    rows_A = len(A)
    cols_A = len(A[0])
    rows_B = len(B)
    cols_B = len(B[0]) if isinstance(B[0], list) else 1
    
    # Kim tra iu kin nhn ma trn
    if cols_A != rows_B:
        raise ValueError(f"Kch thc khng ph hp: ({rows_A}x{cols_A}) v ({rows_B}x{cols_B})")
    
    # Nhn ma trn
    C = create_matrix(rows_A, cols_B)
    for i in range(rows_A):
        for j in range(cols_B):
            for k in range(cols_A):
                C[i][j] += A[i][k] * B[k][j]
    
    # Nu ma trn kt qu ch c 1 ct, tr v vector
    if cols_B == 1:
        return [row[0] for row in C]
    
    return C


def print_matrix(A):
    """Hm in ma trn"""
    for row in A:
        print(f"{'  '.join(f'{x:.6f}' for x in row)}")


def inverse(P):
    """Tnh ma trn nghch o bng phng php Gauss - Jordan"""
    n = len(P)
    
    # To ma trn m rng [P | I]
    P_augmented = []
    for i in range(n):
        row = P[i][:]
        for j in range(n):
            if i == j:
                row.append(1.0)
            else:
                row.append(0.0)
        P_augmented.append(row)
    
    # Bin i Gauss - Jordan
    for i in range(n):
        # Tm pivot
        max_val = abs(P_augmented[i][i])
        max_row = i
        for k in range(i + 1, n):
            if abs(P_augmented[k][i]) > max_val:
                max_val = abs(P_augmented[k][i])
                max_row = k
        
        # Hon i hng
        if max_row != i:
            P_augmented[i], P_augmented[max_row] = P_augmented[max_row], P_augmented[i]
        
        # Chun ha hng pivot
        pivot = P_augmented[i][i]
        for j in range(i, 2*n):
            P_augmented[i][j] /= pivot
        
        # Kh tt c cc hng khc
        for k in range(n):
            if k != i:
                factor = P_augmented[k][i]
                for j in range(i, 2*n):
                    P_augmented[k][j] -= factor * P_augmented[i][j]
    
    # Ly ma trn nghch o
    P_inverse = []
    for i in range(n):
        P_inverse.append(P_augmented[i][n:])
    
    return P_inverse


def transpose(A):
    """Tnh ma trn chuyn v"""

    # Kim tra nu A l vector
    if not isinstance(A[0], list):
        return [[a] for a in A]  # Chuyn vector hng thnh vector ct
    
    # Tnh ma trn chuyn v
    rows = len(A)
    cols = len(A[0])
    A_T = [[0 for _ in range(rows)] for _ in range(cols)]
    
    for i in range(rows):
        for j in range(cols):
            A_T[j][i] = A[i][j]
    
    return A_T

def sum_of_squares(values):
    """Tnh tng bnh phng ca list"""
    return sum(x * x for x in values)

def ols(X, y):
    """
    Hm trin khai OLS  tnh h s hi quy tuyn tnh
    Cng thc: beta = (X^T X)^(-1) X^T y
    """
     # Tnh ma trn X^T
    X_T = transpose(X)
    
    # Tnh (X^T X)
    X_T_X = matrix_multiply(X_T, X)
    X_T_X_inverse = inverse(X_T_X)
    
    # Tnh ma trn (X^T y)
    X_T_y = matrix_multiply(X_T, y)
    
    # Tnh h s beta
    beta = matrix_multiply(X_T_X_inverse, X_T_y)
    
    return beta


def predict(X, coefficients):
    """ Tnh gi tr d on y_hat = X * beta """

    # Thm ct hng s 1  tnh h s chn
    X_with_intercept = [[1] + row for row in X]
    
    # Tnh gi tr d on y_hat = X * beta
    y_pred = []
    for row in X_with_intercept:
        pred = 0
        for j in range(len(coefficients)):
            pred += row[j] * coefficients[j]
        y_pred.append(pred)
    
    return y_pred


def evaluate_model(y_true, y_pred):
    """
    Tnh ch s nh gi m hnh: chn chun vector phn d
    """

    # Tnh cc phn d
    residuals = [y_true[i] - y_pred[i] for i in range(len(y_true))]

    # print("Phn d:", residuals)
    # print("Gi tr d on:", y_pred)
    # print("Gi tr thc t:", y_true)

    # Tnh chun vector ca phn d
    residuals_norm = math.sqrt(sum_of_squares(residuals))
    
    return residuals_norm

y = df[target].values.tolist()

# Lu c trng tt nht (tn, chun vector phn d, h s)
best_feature = None

for feature in features:
    print(f"\nc trng: {feature}")
    
    # Ly ra gi tr ca c trng hin ti
    X_single_feature = [[row[features.index(feature)]] for row in X]
    
    # Thm ct hng s 1  tnh h s chn w0
    X_single_feature_with_intercept = [[1] + row for row in X_single_feature]
    
    # Tnh cc h s
    coefficients_single = ols(X_single_feature_with_intercept, y)
    
    # Tnh gi tr d on
    y_pred_single = predict(X_single_feature, coefficients_single)
    
    # nh gi m hnh
    residuals_norm_single = evaluate_model(y, y_pred_single)

    # Lu c trng m m hnh th hin tt nht
    if best_feature is None or residuals_norm_single < best_feature[1]:
        best_feature = (feature, residuals_norm_single, coefficients_single)
    
    # In kt qu
    print(f"\tH s chn (Intercept): {coefficients_single[0]:.5f}")
    print(f"\tH s ca x_1: {coefficients_single[1]:.5f}")
    print(f"\tChun vector phn d: {residuals_norm_single:.5f}")

# In c trng tt nht
if best_feature:
    print(f"\nc trng tt nht: {best_feature[0]}, vi chun vector phn d: {best_feature[1]:.5f}")

# Phng trnh hi quy
if best_feature:
    feature = best_feature[0]
    coefficient = best_feature[2]
    equation_best = f"loyalty_score = {coefficient[0]:.5f} {'+' if coefficient[1] >= 0 else '-'} {abs(coefficient[1]):.5f} * {feature}"
    print(f"\nPhng trnh hi quy cho c trng tt nht ({feature}):")
    print(equation_best)

e. Thit k mt m hnh hi quy tuyn tnh khc vi nhng m hnh trn m cho kt qu tt nht.

V ta ch cn tnh cht tuyn tnh cho cc tham s $w_i$, cn $x_i$ c th bt k dng no nn ta tin hnh mt s php bin i ln $x_i$, chng hn nh: bnh phng, lp phng, ly cn bc hai, cn bc 3, ly log.

Ta tin hnh thay i cho tng c trng v chn ra php bin i tt nht cho c trng , t ta c c tp cc php bin i tt nht tng ng cho tng c trng xy dng m hnh hi quy tuyn tnh mi vi kt qu tt hn cc m hnh trc .

Kt qu cc php bin i tt nht l:

  • age: Logarith
  • annual_income: Bnh phng
  • purchase_amount: Gc
  • purchase_frequency: Gc

M hnh hi quy:

loyalty_score = -7.7399237400 + 3.1074771436 * age (Logarith) - 0.0000000001 * annual_income (Bnh phng) + 0.0097509272 * purchase_amount (Gc) - 0.0261511036 * purchase_frequency (Gc)

Chun vector phn d: 2.8604340657 (e) < 2.9664091744 (c) < 3.1584141192 (d)

# Ln lt lu cc phng php bin i tt nht cho tng c trng
best_methods = {}

for feature in features:
    print(f"\nc trng: {feature}")
    
    # Ly d liu ca c trng hin ti
    feature_data = df[feature].values.tolist()
    
    # Bin i d liu
    transformations = {
        'Gc': feature_data,
        'Bnh phng': [x ** 2 for x in feature_data],
        'Cn bc hai': [math.sqrt(x) if x >= 0 else 0 for x in feature_data],
        'Logarith': [math.log(x) if x > 0 else 0 for x in feature_data],
        'Lp phng': [x ** 3 for x in feature_data],
        'Cn bc ba': [x ** (1/3) for x in feature_data]
    }
    
    # V biu  cho tng bin i  so snh trc quan
    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 20))
    for i, (transform_name, transformed_data) in enumerate(transformations.items()):
        plt.subplot(3, 2, i + 1)
        plt.scatter(transformed_data, df[target], alpha=0.5)
        plt.title(f'{transform_name} ca {feature} v {target}')
        plt.xlabel(transform_name)
        plt.ylabel(target)
        plt.grid()
    
    # Tnh chun vector phn d cho tng bin i
    for transform_name, transformed_data in transformations.items():

        # Tch d liu thnh
        X_transformed = [[x] for x in transformed_data]
        
        # Thm ct hng s 1  tnh h s chn w0
        X_transformed_with_intercept = [[1] + row for row in X_transformed]
        
        # Tnh cc h s
        coefficients_transformed = ols(X_transformed_with_intercept, y)
        
        # Tnh gi tr d on
        y_pred_transformed = predict(X_transformed, coefficients_transformed)

        # nh gi m hnh
        residuals_norm_transformed = evaluate_model(y, y_pred_transformed)

        # In kt qu
        # print(f"\t{transform_name}:")
        # print(f"\t\tH s chn (Intercept): {coefficients_transformed[0]:.5f}")
        # print(f"\t\tH s ca {feature}: {coefficients_transformed[1]:.5f}")
        # print(f"\t\tChun vector phn d: {residuals_norm_transformed:.5f}")

        # So snh gia cc bin i v in ra kt qu tt nht
        if transform_name == 'Gc':
            best_transform = transform_name
            best_residual = residuals_norm_transformed
        else:
            if residuals_norm_transformed < best_residual:
                best_transform = transform_name
                best_residual = residuals_norm_transformed
    
    print(f"Bin i tt nht: {best_transform}, vi chun vector ca phn d: {best_residual:.5f}")
    best_methods[feature] = best_transform


# In ra cc phng php bin i tt nht cho tng c trng
print("\nCc phng php bin i tt nht cho tng c trng:")
for feature, method in best_methods.items():
    print(f"\t{feature}: {method}")
